Detailed Description

template<typename VarArray1, typename VarArray2, typename Operator = NeqIterated, BOOL is_reversed = false>
struct VecCountDynamic< VarArray1, VarArray2, Operator, is_reversed >

constraints;hamming Description The constraint

hamming(X,Y,c)

ensures that the hamming distance between X and Y is at least c. That is, that the size of the set {i | X[i] != y[i]} is greater than or equal to c.
